title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Fleet Aircraft 50K
description:
In this video we will look at version 1.0 of the  Fleet Aircraft 50K which is currently in beta. The aircraft has a lot of potential but there is still a lot of work to do. Graphically it all looks really nice but the buttons inside the aircraft are not working and the only way to control the aircraft including starting it is by using the keyboard or joystick

If you also want to give the aircraft a try you can download it from the site below:
https://flightsim.to/file/17074/fleet-aircraft-50k-tundra-cargo-w-original-cockpit-panel
